item.title: Are The Kansas City Chiefs Considering Alternate Uniforms?
item.description: Don't expect the Kansas City Chiefs to get an alternate uniform anytime soon, though their owner appears to be warming up to the idea.

item.title: New York Jets Unveil “The Classic” Throwback Uniforms
item.description: Although it’s only been five years since they moved away from the design, the New York Jets unveiled a familiar throwback uniform that will be worn against the Buffalo Bills on Monday Night Football on Oct. 14.
